{"about_the_game":"Originally released in 1984, this unique shooter saw players take on the role of a pilot of an out-dated Cosmic Cruiser, fighting to rescue the crew of a distant space station that had been captured by a raiding party from the sinister Rallom Empire. Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Use your ship's large roof-mounted space cannon to blast open portals on the spinning space station, allowing you to enter and rescue crew members, but watch out: alien warriors swarm the station, and your handheld laser gun has limited ammo!<br><br><br>This enhanced version introduces a number of modern features to this retro classic, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Saving/loading the game at any point<br></li><li> Support for most modern game controllers<br></li><li> Full control remapping<br></li><li> Image scaling and smoothing options</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1659621813","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080160/page.bg.jpg?t=1659621813","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1659621813","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2080160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1659621813","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Originally released in 1984, this unique shooter saw players take on the role of a pilot of an out-dated Cosmic Cruiser, fighting to rescue the crew of a distant space station that had been captured by a raiding party from the sinister Rallom Empire. Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<h2